  "detailed_description": "<strong> !!!!About English Translation!!!! </strong><br>As for English, the system messages have been translated.<br>For conversational text, machine translation is used, so there are some unnatural points in the translation. Also, parts of the conversation may appear in a different language. Please be aware of this.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Touhou:Shooting Star -Touhou Ryuseitan</h2><br>As a wizard \"Marisa Kirisame\", Fly in the Gensokyo!<br>This is fun game of \"Touhou Project\"!<br>Let's play \"Danmaku\"!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >３D Danmaku Battle</h2>Fly and fight in the Gensokyo.<br>3-directyional bullets is reaching to you.<br>Avoid bullets and shot down enemys!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/21f8d89fc9288496fb0e094908405f16.poster.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/21f8d89fc9288496fb0e094908405f16.webm?t=1677780786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/21f8d89fc9288496fb0e094908405f16.mp4?t=1677780786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spell Card</h2>Boss enemys use \"Spell Card\".<br>Defeat their beautiful danmaku and Get ther Spell Card!<br>Analyze and avoid characteristical bullet patten.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/ddca60553705fb0dcc52e36f32232171.poster.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/ddca60553705fb0dcc52e36f32232171.webm?t=1677780786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/ddca60553705fb0dcc52e36f32232171.mp4?t=1677780786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/c829120f18c571036c23204ebeb19bf7.poster.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/c829120f18c571036c23204ebeb19bf7.webm?t=1677780786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/c829120f18c571036c23204ebeb19bf7.mp4?t=1677780786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Develop your weapon</h2>Get materials from defeated enemys and develop more strong weapon, armor, and spell card.<br>Make your own equipments set.<br>Each weapon has parameters and bullet.<br>Each Armor has parameters and skills and appearance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/23b738722602a66c9c5fd5710047118a.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/7c414993836c39ae9e5365290563cc26.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quest</h2>This game includes more 30 quests! <br>Enemy boss character is more than 10 !<br>And every quest has sub targets.<br>Let's try \"No damage clear\",\"Time attack\",\"Get all spell cards\" and so on.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/41be567a8885496adb70f438aa9f884e.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Talk in Gensokyo</h2>There are many characters of \"Touhou Project\" in the village and can talk to them.<br>Let's talk as Marisa!<br>There is original illust of characters of Touhou Project.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/f81265721da7057d4c3022dc7d2151b7.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boutique</h2>You can change Marisa's cloth.<br>Find your favorite cloth and fly in Gensokyo.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299420/extras/f7a90a46437df1dc7b76820c451c10c1.avif?t=1677780786\" width=512 height=288 /></span>",
